  "summary": "Malicious code in coloraiz (PyPI)",
  "details": "The package imitates colorama, and places a proxy object over the original colorama module that on every usage executes a remote code. The remote script installs a backdoor through legitimate tunnelling software and upload access credentials to the attacker.\n\n\n---\n\nCategory: MALICIOUS - The campaign has clearly malicious intent, like infostealers.\n\n\nCampaign: 2025-05-coloraiz\n\n\nReasons (based on the campaign):\n\n\n - impersonation\n\n\n - clones-real-package\n\n\n - action-hidden-in-lib-usage\n\n\n - backdoor\n\n\n - Downloads and executes a remote malicious script.\n\n",
